Package com.zendesk.sdk.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppVersion
    This class allows you to determine the Application's version information
    Attachment
    This is a model class for a Attachment object that will be created by the ZendeskRequestProvider as part of User.
    Comment
    This is a model class for a Comment object that will be created by the ZendeskRequestProvider as part of CommentsResponse.
    CommentResponse
    This is a model class for a CommentResponse object that will be fetched by the ZendeskRequestProvider as part of CommentsResponse.
    CreateRequest
    This is a model class for a request that will be submitted by the FeedbackDialog when it has been configured with a Zendesk feedback connector.
    CustomField
    CustomFields model which allows for custom data to be set on a request
    DeviceInfo
    Wrapper for device information.
    EndUserComment
    EndUserComment object is used to model the difference the API for updating a Request has with fetching a list of Comments for a given request.
    MemoryInformation
    This class is used to get information about the physical memory (RAM) that is available on the device
    Organization
    This is a model class for a Organization object that will be created by the ZendeskRequestProvider as part of CommentsResponse.
    Request
    This is a model class for a Request object that will be created by the RequestProvider.
    UpdateRequestWrapper
    UpdateRequestWrapper object is used to model the payload required when posting an update to a request.
    User
    This is a model class for a user that will be created by the ZendeskRequestProvider as part of CommentsResponse.
    Via
    This is a model class for a Via object that will be created by the RequestProvider as part of Request
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AuthenticationType
    Enum to track the authentication type for a given app configuration Created by Zendesk on 18/11/2014.
